title: UFYB 51: Listener Q & A Vol. 4
itunes:title: Listener Q & A Vol. 4
description:
This week, I am back with another round of questions from all of you and my tough-love answers. Today, we’re digging into a number of topics such as dealing with ‘problem’ coworkers, letting go of shame around past mistakes, feeling more lovable, and helping others.

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfckyourbrain.com/51
